==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Spelt
<hw>Spelt</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>spelt</ets>, fr. L.
<ets>spelta</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A species of grain
(<spn>Triticum Spelta</spn>) much cultivated for food in Germany and
Switzerland; -- called also <altname>German wheat</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spelt</ent>⟦br⟧

